msgctxt "sn17.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → pāti 1 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Suvaṇṇapātisutta → pātivaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Suvaṇṇapātisutta"
msgstr "11. A Golden Bowl"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.233"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn17.11:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.11:1.3"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi:"
msgstr "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a certain person, I understand:"

msgctxt "sn17.11:1.4"
msgid "‘na cāyamāyasmā suvaṇṇapātiyāpi rūpiyacuṇṇaparipūrāya hetu sampajānamusā bhāseyyā’ti."
msgstr "‘This venerable would not tell a deliberate lie even for the sake of a golden bowl filled with silver powder.’"

msgctxt "sn17.11:1.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ passāmi aparena samayena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ sampajānamusā bhāsantaṃ."
msgstr "But some time later I see them tell a deliberate lie because their mind is overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "sn17.11:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.11:1.7"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.11:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
